Upgraded Isiolo Aiport to host miraa export base. Miraa farmers will soon start exporting their crop from the newly upgraded Isiolo International Airport. Kenya Airports Authority said plans were underway to relocate the crop&rsquo;s export base from Nairobi&rsquo;s Wilson Airport to Isiolo following completion of the airport&rsquo;s upgrade. Managing Director Johnny Anderson said the airport was now ready for use.&nbsp;